In Annex I to Regulation (EEC) No 1324/68:    (a) subheading 04.04 E I b) 2 is hereby deleted;
(b) subheading 04.04 E I b) 5 is hereby amended as follows:      - the term "ButterkĂ¤se" is inserted before "Danbo",
- the term "Tilsit" is inserted after "Saint-Paulin".
